un with so much to see and do at walt disney world resort this summer you and your family can make magical vacation memories to last a lifetime enjoy  theme parks and  water parks each with immersive attractions and experiences plus explore disney springs a breezy promenade brimming with restaurants shops and entertainment disney’s animal kingdom park delve into the magic of nature embark on a tour of a lush savanna that’s home to exotic animals on kilimanjaro safaris avoid the clutches of the mythic yeti aboard a runaway train at expedition everest and beginning may   discover the aweinspiring land and immersive attractions of pandora – the world of avatar disney’s hollywood studios thrill to hollywood at its best race la’s freeways on rock ‘n’ roller coaster starring aerosmith test your aim at toy story mania hurtle up and down the twilight zone tower of terror or feel the force during star wars a galactic spectacular and starting may   celebrate tunes from cars toy story and more with the music of pixar live epcot travel the globe into outer space and beyond fly over scenic wonder of the world on soarin’ sail on a musical ride through arendelle on frozen ever after rev across rough terrain at test track or behold the story of our planet during illuminations reflections of earth plus through may   enjoy the epcot international flower  garden festival magic kingdom park make dreams come true in a world of fantasy race through a diamond mine aboard seven dwarfs mine train brave a spinetingling tour of the haunted mansion or be immersed in enchanted storytelling with the once upon a time nighttime show and conclude your day in a spectacular way with the new happily ever after fireworks show disney’s typhoon lagoon water park splash land into a storm of excitement embark on a thrilling voyage along miss adventure falls ride a gnarly wave at the typhoon lagoon surf pool catch air on a coastertype ride atop slippery slides at crush ‘n’ gusher—or gather the group for a scenic rafting excursion past rocky caverns at gangplank falls disney’s blizzard beach water park find frosty fun at this watery wonderland feel your cares melt away as you glide on an inner tube at cross country creek plunge  stories on a nearvertical drop at summit plummet or race against a friend at the downhill double dipper plus little ones can splash and play at ketchakiddee creek disney springs enjoy eclectic dining and shopping at over  unique venues explore brandname boutiques like uniqlo and zara and pick up keepsakes at world of disney find live entertainment around every corner—and be dazzled by cirque du soleil and savor the dining delights of stk morimoto asia and frontera cocina vacation planning tips pick up some tips for your upcoming trip with our planning guides including information on fun attractions and experiences for little ones tweens and grandparents park magic ticket  per day total price   tax more information beginning of tooltip content the park magic ticket price is valid for one theme park per day for each day of the ticket price is per person and does not include tax end of tooltip content select tickets share beginning of tooltip content pinteresttwittergooglefacebookemail end of tooltip content for assistance with your walt disney world visit please call   am to  pm eastern time guests under  years of age must have parent or guardian permission to call footer links parks  ticketsmagic kingdom parkepcotdisneys hollywood studiosdisneys animal kingdom parkwater parkspark hourspark ticketsannual passesplaces to stayresort hotelsspecial offersvacation packagesthings to domake dining reservationsall diningdining plansattractionscharacter experiencesentertainmentevents  toursshopsspas  fitness centerssports and recreationactivity photoscirque du soleil – la noubadisney springsdisneys boardwalkespn wide world of sportshelpcontact ushelp centerfrequently asked questionsguests with disabilitiesguest servicesdisney parks moms panelguest sa