e corporate issuer solutions the legal transfer form is available in the forms section of this website q is there a fee to transfer shares a yes there is a fee to transfer ownership of the walt disney company shares  to debit per account and  to credit per account please make all checks payable to “broadridge” example transfer from john smith cust sarah smith utmaca  to debit shares transfer to sarah smith  to credit shares a total of  to transfer shares in the example above the legal transfer form is available in the forms section of this website q how do i access my disney shareholder account a to access your disney shareholder account click here please note that you will be leaving disneycom to access your account information you will be required to register as a user on the system to access your shareholder information disney annual meeting of shareholders q when and where was the  annual meeting of shareholders a the walt disney company’s annual meeting was held on wednesday march   in denver colorado q where can i listen to the audio webcast of the meeting a click here to listen to the audio webcast q where can i view the photos taken at the meeting a photos taken at the  annual meeting of shareholders are available at wwwshareholderphotoscom disney stock q can i buy or sell stock directly through disney a yes you can buy and sell shares directly through the walt disney company investment plan the walt disney company investment plan prospectus and enrollment form are available in the forms section of this website additional information regarding the walt disney company investment plan is available at wwwdisneyshareholdercom q where are your shares traded a disney common stock is traded on the new york stock exchange q what is the ticker symbol a dis q what is the cusip number a  dividends q when did disney declare the most recent dividend payment a on june   the walt disney company board of directors declared a semiannual cash dividend of  per share payable july   to shareholders of record at the close of business on july   q i am enrolled in the walt disney company investment plan and want to know when my dividends reinvested a the reinvestment of your dividends will be completed within five business days of the dividend payment date q if i am not enrolled in the walt disney company investment plan how will my dividend be paid a the dividend is paid by check or may be directly deposited into a bank account most domestic banks and financial institutions allow for direct deposit for more information regarding direct deposit you can access your account online at wwwdisneyshareholdercom or you can contact us at our toll free number disney  although the amount of your dividend may be negligible we encourage you to keep your account up to date by cashing your check there are abandoned property laws that require us to remit dividends and stock holdings for inactive accounts q i never received my dividend check how do i request a replacement a please allow the post office at least  mailing days to deliver your check if you never received your check or it was misplaced you will need to request a replacement you can request a replacement by accessing your account online at wwwdisneyshareholdercom you may also contact our transfer agent broadridge corporate issuer solutions to request a replacement check broadridge’s contact information is located in the transfer agent section of this faq if you are submitting your replacement request in writing at least one of the registered owners must sign the letter replacement checks are mailed within  business days once a request has been submitted please note there is a fee to replace dividend and sale checks q how can i have my dividend reinvested a dividend reinvestment is offered through the walt disney company investment plan you may request enrollment materials online at wwwdisneyshareholdercom or you can contact us at our toll free number disney  stock split history q when has disney 