ome to worldclass teams of app and game developers licensing and retail experts a leading retail business disney store artists and storytellers and technologists who inspire imaginations around the world leadership dcpi leaders lend their experience and expertise across a variety of industries to bring disney stories and characters to life through innovative and engaging physical products and digital experiences james pitarochairman disney consumer products and interactive media james pitaro chairman disney consumer products and interactive mediajames pitaro was named chairman disney consumer products and interactive media dcpi in february  where he oversees the company’s creation of physical and digital experiences across more than  categories pitaro and his team bring to life the characters and stories of four iconic brands—disney pixar star wars and marvel – through the world’s largest licensing business across toys apparel and home goods the world’s largest children’s book publisher a robust digital game slate including mobile and console experiences and approximately  disney store locations around the world also under pitaro’s leadership is the team at maker studios as well as cuttingedge technologists who manage disney’s web and social media presence in addition his team manages the company’s relationships with retailers globally pitaro previously served as president disney interactive where he successfully led the turnaround of the gaming and digital media division of the walt disney company prior to his roles at disney pitaro served as vice president and head of yahoo media where he was responsible for guiding the strategic growth and continued development of yahoo’s media properties including yahoo sports and yahoo music he was credited with leading those businesses to their positions as the number one online sports and music destinations pitaro was also vice president of business affairs for launch media inc and practiced law at several new york firms pitaro holds a bachelor of science in economics from cornell university and a juris doctor from st john’s law school download jpg download pdf molly adamsexecutive vice president global merchandising and product development dcpi  walt disney parks and resorts molly adams executive vice president global merchandising and product development dcpi  walt disney parks and resortsas executive vice president global merchandising and product development adams brings more than  years of retail and product experience to her role adams leads a centralized integrated merchandising and product development team that spans business models for disney consumer products and interactive media’s licensed and vertical retail and walt disney parks and resorts’ merchandise adams and her team are responsible for delivering a consistent disney brand message to consumers through a comprehensive range of creative quality products that continue the walt disney companys stories far beyond the theatrical or television experience prior to leading merchandising and product development for dcpi and wdpr adams spent more than five years as part of the disney store leadership team serving as executive vice president global product development senior vice president disney store north america and vice president and general manager disney store north america adams has an additional five years of disney store merchandise experience from a previous stint for a total of plus years at the walt disney company earlier in her career adams held leadership positions in various department stores entertainment and specialty retail organizations with a broad range of responsibilities including design creative and merchandising adams is a member of the dean’s advisory council for the haslam college of business at university of tennessee and has a bachelors of science in business administration from the university of tennessee download jpg download pdf luis fernandezsenior vice president global creative dcpi  walt disney