white’s leadership dcpi’s technology organization is innovating to transform both consumerfacing and backofhouse programs and initiatives and leveraging cutting edge technologies in new and different ways from a unique approach to the cloud to cutting edge exploration of artificial intelligence and machine learning white’s team is leveraging transformational innovation to change the way consumers experience the walt disney company’s stories and characters prior to his current role white was the chief technology officer at disney interactive where he led technical direction and platform development for apps games and much of the company’s digital footprint additionally he oversaw the development of a portfolio of consumer products cloud infrastructure business intelligence data suites mobile network and proprietary game engine technology before joining disney interactive in  white served as cto and cio of the apollo group where he led the development of academic social networks mobile applications and the creation of an educationaladaptive learning platform for third parties and universities from  to  white worked at yahoo where he held senior positions in product development engineering and global operations previously white worked in technology at geocities until the company was acquired by yahoo in  white holds a bachelor of arts degree from the ohio state university download jpg download pdf suzanne wilsondeputy general counsel the walt disney company chief counsel suzanne wilson deputy general counsel the walt disney company chief counselwilson joined the walt disney company as deputy general counsel in  overseeing the company’s attorneys responsible for worldwide legal oversight of copyright trademark patent consumer products licensing online and console games online properties and antipiracy enforcement matters as the head lawyer for disney consumer products and interactive media wilson provides strategic legal advice to dcpis executive management team and manages the group that provides legal support to the various business operations within the interactive media segment of dcpi prior to joining disney in  wilson was a partner at the law firm arnold  porter llp wilson holds a bachelor of arts degree in economics from the university of california at berkeley and a juris doctor magna cum laude from harvard law school download jpg download pdf view more our businesses licensing the licensing business is aligned around five strategic brand priorities disney media classics  entertainment disney  pixar animation disney princess frozen  tinker bell lucasfilm and marvel view more retail disney retail encompasses disney store worldwide – which operates more than  stores and related ecommerce sites in north america europe and asia – and integrated retail which consolidates all north america retail channels into one seamless integrated team across the walt disney company view more games  interactive experiences the disney games  interactive experiences business is comprised of internally developed licensed and codeveloped mobile products as well as licensed console video games these leading worldclass experiences draw upon the most beloved stories and characters from disney pixar marvel and star wars to create highquality interactive game experiences across mobile and console platforms for fans of all ages view more publishing and digital media dcpi’s publishing and digital media business unit includes disney publishing worldwide and an extensive digital media network that spans mobile video influencers shortform content and microcontent the business is focused on drawing a new generation into disney stories and building original content ip and brands while attracting engaged audiences across publishing and social platforms view more citizenship being a good corporate citizen is a timehonored tradition at the walt disney company through contributions collaborations with local organizations inkind gifts and volunteering disney cast members help to strengthen communities and brighten the lives of families around the world at disney consumer products and interactive media being a good corporate citizen also includes focusing on the environmental stewardship of our products in collaboration with our top licensees through programs like the smartpackaging initiative promoting healthier lifestyles through disney’s healthy living commitment creating impactful cause marketing initiatives and content that inspire kids and families to join us in creating a brighter tomorrow reaching out to community organizations with product donations   learn more microsoft personalized ad preferences to opt out of personalized ads in this browser your browser history must allow firstparty and thirdparty cookies and you must have your browsing experience set to not delete browsing history on exit instructions for enabling cookies and configuring your browsing history may be available in your browsers settings privacy or help documentation sign in hold on… we’re sorry but this didn’t work you can’t turn off personalized ads right now because your browser is currently blocking thirdparty cookies we can help you fix this issue let’s get started depending on what browser you use open options or settings make sure that thirdparty cookies are not blocked anymore to find out how search your browser’s help revisit httpchoicemicrosoftcomoptout and then on the “personalized ads in this browser” tile click off ext about our ads to create a more customized online experience some of the ads you may receive on microsoft websites and apps are tailored to your previous activities searches and site visits youre in control and heres where you can make the advertising choice thats right for you ext where can i learn more about advertising on microsoft websites and apps microsoft partners with oath appnexus and other third party service providers to help present customized content and display advertisements on msn outlookcom and other we